nd induces apoptosis in cells that highly express CD38, including multiple myeloma cells.[L13290,L13296] It has a long duration of action as it is given every 1-4 weeks.[L13290,L13296] Patients should be counselled regarding the risk of hypersensitivity, neutropenia, thrombocytopenia, embryo-fetal toxicity, and interferences with cross-matching and red blood cell antibody screening.[L13290,L13296]', 'DrugBank', 0, 0, 0);
